description:
We all know the story of Noah and the Ark. But what is it about his story that manages to intrigue both youth and elderly alike?

According to Pastor Matt, there is an explanation behind the transcendent charm of this story. Even when no one else would listen, Noah continued to follow God’s lead. And by the end of the catastrophic flood, Noah’s family and the animals of the world were preserved. The circumstances surrounding Noah’s Ark would bear major ramifications for God’s people, even to this very day.
